thread.title_full: Chicago ends year with 762 homicides, the most in 2 decades in the city

author: The Associated Press
title: Chicago ends year with 762 homicides, the most in 2 decades in the city
text: The data released Sunday are staggering, even for those who followed the steady news accounts of weekends ending with dozens of shootings and monthly death tolls that hadn't been seen in years.
